A LibreOffice-safe formula is:
`=IF(I2="","",IFERROR(LEFT(I2,FIND(" - ",I2)-1),I2))`

This returns blank for blank input, extracts the left portion when `" - "` exists, and falls back to the original cell if the delimiter is absent.
Code:
